originalText.text:
I have been a patient of Dr Page for about 8 years and I just left his office late this afternoon.  The office is close to major subway lines and there is also a bus stop directly across the street.

The office staff is very professional, courteous and genuinely cares about their patients.  I am always impressed when I visit the office that Dr Page seems to have the latest technology and new dental instruments.  I really like that after my dental cleanings that I am thoroughly examined by Dr Page, himself, and not an assistant.

His hygienist, Simone, cannot be beat.  She's diligent, thorough and fun, too.  Gone are the days of employees who don't take pride in their work when it comes to this dental practice!

I would travel further than I do now to go to a dentist who doesn't attempt to "sell you procedures" that really are not required.  Or to go to one who doesn't bill things to  your insurance that weren't done.  Can we say Dr Page is honest?  YES!

I highly recommend you giving this office your trust and business for you and to your family.  I have visited when children are there.  They are leaving with smiles on their faces.  Obviously, Dr Page and his team know how to calm one's fears!

Enjoy your visits!

originalText.text: Dr. Page has been my dentist for many years.  I wouldn't hesitate to recommend him to any of my friends.  I can't say I love having cavities filled or my teeth cleaned,  but he and his assistants make the experience as painless and pleasant as possible.  He's highly professional and very experienced---an excellent dentist.

originalText.text: I have been going to Dr. Page for over 20 years and every time I go for my 6 month cleaning, I remember why I travel from NJ to NY to go to the dentist.  Dr. Page greets everyone as if he is their friend, his staff is professional and courteous.  What I really admire about Dr. Page is that he is patient and gentle.  Every time I do go for my normal visit, he always educates me about how I should take care of my teeth.  His equipment is alway up-to-date state of-the-art.  The facility is always extremely clean and comfortable.  And, even the parking is not a problem, the staff will refill the meters if necessary!!  (that's an extra valuable customer service gesture) and you always get a nice "goodie" bag from him, toothbrush, floss and mouthwash!  In all of my years going to Dr. Page, my appointment has always been ON TIME!!   My whole family goes to his practice.   I always recommend Dr. Page to my clients and friends.....   He is especially good if you are one that is afraid of going to dentist.... That's why I started going to him in the first place.

originalText.text: Dr. Gregory Page is one of the most talented dentist in the city of New York. There's absolutely nothing to fear when you need extensive dental work done. I needed an emergency root canal and was obviously worried about pain control. Dr. Page assured me that they would be little or no pain and then begin to work on my root canal. I am so happy to report that everything went fine and today I am pain free. Like I said, Dr. Gregory Page is the most talented dentist in the city of New York.
